<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.8">
<l>vaṭṭa vāycciṟu tūtai yōṭuci ṟucuḷa kummaṇa luṅkoṇ</l>
<l>ṭiṭṭa māviḷai yāṭu vōṅkaḷaic ciṟṟi līṭaḻit teṉpayaṉ</l>
<l>toṭṭutait tunali yēlkaṇ ṭāycuṭarc cakka raṅkaiyi lēntiṉāy</l>
<l>kaṭṭi yuṅkait tāliṉ ṉāmai yaṟiti yēkaṭal vaṇṇaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is the use of thoroughly destroying the little [sand] house [made by] us,</l>
<l>who play as [we] please, with small earthen pots with a round opening,</l>
<l rend="indent">small winnowing fans and sand?</l>
<l>Look, do not destroy [them] by touching and kicking [them]!</l>
<l rend="indent">O You who carry an effulgent discus in [Your] hand!</l>
<l>Do you not know that if [the heart] becomes bitter, even jaggery will not be sweet,</l>
<l rend="indent">O ocean-hued One!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
